The paper discusses the security and privacy concerns related to machine learning models, specifically deep neural networks. It evaluates the state-of-the-art model extraction attack and proposes a defense mechanism. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). However, the paper also involves topics related to machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), and software engineering (cs.SE).
